snippet.textDisplay: Dear Rafaqat Ali Khan. It was apleasure meeting you and your son Bakht Ali Khan in Dublin today. I am a great fan of you and love your Kalam Tu Kuja Man Kuja. I espeically created a video in Madina and Macca and dubbed your kalam on it. I hope you will watch it as you promised and would like it. I think your voice is meant to read kalaam for Mohammad sallahowalawassallam. May god bless you both. Sabih Mirza from Waterford Ireland
